name: Charles-Hubert- Paris Brass Mechanical Hunter Case Pocket Watch #3804
description:
During the past decade  Charles-Hubert  Paris has established itself as a high-quality yet affordable watch manufacturer.  With both modern and classic styling to choose from as well as our unparalleled lifetime warranty against defects  Charles-Hubert  Paris is the most intelligent choice.

This pocket watch by Charles-Hubert  Paris features a skeleton dial with Roman numerals  17 Jewel mechanical movement  48mm case and presents in a deluxe gift box.
